パッケージの使用
org.sxb.data.redis.core

  • org.sxb.data.redis.coreを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.data.redis.cache
    Package providing a Redis implementation for Spring cache abstraction.
    org.sxb.data.redis.connection
    Connection package providing low-level abstractions for interacting with the various Redis 'drivers'/libraries.
    org.sxb.data.redis.connection.jedis
    Connection package for Jedis library.
    org.sxb.data.redis.core
    Core package for integrating Redis with Spring concepts.
    org.sxb.data.redis.core.script  
    org.sxb.data.redis.support.atomic
    Small toolkit mirroring the java.util.atomic package in Redis.
    org.sxb.data.redis.support.collections
    Package providing implementations for most of the java.util collections on top of Redis.
    org.sxb.session.data.redis
